.PP
.Vb 2
\&    git clone https://github.com/ingydotnet/git\-subrepo /path/to/git\-subrepo
\&    echo \*(Aqsource /path/to/git\-subrepo/.rc\*(Aq >> ~/.bashrc
.Ve
.PP
The complete \*(L"Installation Instructions\*(R" can be found below.
.PP
